14
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:13,000
Another idea for the future is the four-day working week,

15
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:17,000
where employees work four days for the same money as five.

16
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:21,000
After Covid, many British companies gave the idea a go,

17
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:27,000
but out of the 60 companies taking parts in a four-day working week trial in 2023,

18
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:32,000
how many said they planned to continue with a shorter work week?

19
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:38,000
Was it A, 52% B, 72% or C, 92%.

20
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:44,000
Hmm, I guess 52% of the companies planned to continue with a four-day week.

21
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:48,000
Okay, Beth, I'll reveal the answer later in the programme.

22
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:55,000
Now, whatever Elon Musk thinks, as we've seen it's difficult to make your predictions accurate,

23
